a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Activepieces is best suited for startups, developers, budget conscious teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. IFTTT, meanwhile, shines for consumers, smart home users, simple automations, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2022, Activepieces describes itself as \"Open-source no-code automation platform alternative to Zapier.\" IFTTT, established in 2010, positions itself as \"Simple conditional automation connecting everyday apps and devices.\" With 12 years between them, IFTTT brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Activepieces offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Activepieces** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more features (9 vs 7), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean IFTTT is a poor choice — far from it. IFTTT excels in its own right, particularly for consumers and smart home users.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value fully open-source and self-hostable, go with Activepieces. If extremely simple to use matters more to you, IFTTT is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
